        <p data-role="text">THE BOT&#xAD;TOM LINE: There are some good dishes, but also misses. Over&#xAD;all, both out&#xAD;lets are worth try&#xAD;ing if you are look&#xAD;ing for some&#xAD;thing new. But the cook&#xAD;ing lacks wow &#x2013; ex&#xAD;cept for that pork knuckle.</p>
